              "free_text": [
                " Digitizing error",
                "To ensure that the absolute values obtained were",
                "sensible the 14N(d,p1+2)15N peak was also simulated",
                "using the same parameters but with a known cross-",
                "section (V. Games Porto, etc. Nucl. Phys,A136,385,1969)",
                "and found to agree to within 10% with the experimental",
                "spectrum."
              ]
